criteria.driver_alignment:
Implemented — built and ran full valuation calculations across methods; 
Validate — created sensitivity table showing WACC/growth matrix and quantified valuation impacts; 
Evolve — ran alternative scenarios (recession, accelerated digital mix) that adjust inputs and produced revised bid ranges.

Validate stage — performed sensitivity testing and cross-method checks to assess reasonableness;  
Implement/Represent stages — used DCF, trading comps, and precedent transactions to compare results (internal cross-validation);  
Evolve/Reflect stages — discussed risks and scenario limitations (execution risk, recession, digital upside).
